---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service | Liteworks Co." description="Terms of Service for Liteworks Co., Greater Cincinnati's trusted excavation and sitework experts.">
  <Header client:load />

  <main class="bg-white pt-28 pb-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-[Rajdhani] font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-2">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mb-10">Last updated: March 2026</p>

      <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none space-y-8 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-[Rajdhani] font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-3">1. Agreement to Terms</h2>
          <p>
            By accessing this website, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree, please do not use this site. These terms apply to all visitors and users of liteworksco.com, operated by Liteworks Co., located at 1481 SR 28, Suite 901, Loveland, OH 45140.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-[Rajdhani] font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-3">2. Website Use</h2>
          <p>This website is provided for informational purposes and to allow you to request quotes for our services. You agree not to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-3 space-y-1">
            <li>Use this site for any unlawful purpose</li>
            <li>Submit false or misleading information through our forms</li>
            <li>Attempt to interfere with the proper functioning of the site</li>
            <li>Copy or reproduce site content without our written permission</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-[Rajdhani] font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-3">3. Quote Requests & Service Inquiries</h2>
          <p>
            Submitting a quote request through our website does not constitute a binding contract or guarantee of service. All projects are subject to a site visit, formal estimate, and mutual written agreement before work begins. Prices and availability are subject to change.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-[Rajdhani] font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-3">4. Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p>
            All content on this website — including text, images, logos, and graphics — is the property of Liteworks Co. or its content suppliers and is protected by applicable copyright laws. You may not reproduce, distribute, or create derivative works without our express written permission.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-[Rajdhani] font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-3">5. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
          <p>
            This website and its content are provided "as is" without warranties of any kind, either express or implied. We do not warrant that the site will be error-free, uninterrupted, or free of viruses. Information on this site is for general reference only and may not reflect current pricing, availability, or service areas.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-[Rajdhani] font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-3">6. Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p>
            To the fullest extent permitted by law, Liteworks Co. shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from your use of this website or reliance on information contained herein.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-[Rajdhani] font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-3">7. Third-Party Links</h2>
          <p>
            Our website may contain links to third-party websites. These links are provided for convenience only. We have no control over the content of those sites and accept no responsibility for them.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-[Rajdhani] font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-3">8. Governing Law</h2>
          <p>
            These Terms shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the State of Ohio, without regard to its conflict of law provisions. Any disputes shall be resolved in the courts of Warren County, Ohio.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-[Rajdhani] font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-3">9. Changes to Terms</h2>
          <p>
            We reserve the right to update these Terms at any time. Continued use of the site after changes are posted constitutes acceptance of the new terms.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-[Rajdhani] font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-3">10. Contact</h2>
          <p>
            Questions? Email us at <a href="mailto:team@liteworksco.com" class="text-[#c4d931] hover:underline">team@liteworksco.com</a> or call <a href="tel:5139279675" class="text-[#c4d931] hover:underline">(513) 927-9675</a>.
          </p>
        </section>

      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
